{"tid":1156000,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[NBA]選秀排名揭曉啦 如無意外塘鵝就會揀Zion","createTime":"2019-05-15T10:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T19:11:08.000Z","uid":21357,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fbd72eb0533e0a93a057f397003852bffa825819","tid":1156000,"uid":21357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T10:22:12.000Z","msg":"Zion即將係大量嘅鎂光燈同眾人嘅期待之下進入NBA呢個最高嘅籃球殿堂，究竟佢可唔可以兌現到自己嘅天賦係NBA發光發亮呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPaul Pierce話佢第一季就會入All-Stars，而將來就會變超巨咁話(大家衡量下)<br />\n但宜家亦都講到Zion係唔想去塘鵝嘅，佢心儀嘅球隊係紐約(想當年Okafor都有扭計嘅前車之鑑)<br />\n個人認為佢身體質素真係好勁，但佢除左似隻牛之外，佢真係無咩特別出眾(甚至我覺得佢個模板只係去到Randle而唔係Lebron)，當然可以話睇隊波點養，但呢刻嘅佢我真係唔覺得值得有咁多焦點<br />\n我真係好想睇下大家點睇呢位球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e4906b2f41ef2af7f37d4629cb2f9a42fac383","tid":1156000,"uid":39215,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T10:25:47.000Z","msg":"Paul Pierce條死廢老已經唔駛再理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c